Params: {1: '1', 3: 'Two outlines step out of the shadows.'}
{1: '1', 2: '???', 3: "Kamui of Strike Hawk? Heard he's a feisty one, what's he doing like this?", 4: '2'}
{2: '???', 3: 'He is currently fighting the virus, and it has taken a toll on his capacity.', 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: 'When he loses hold, his frame will become empowered by the virus and also begin attacking humans.', 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: "If that's so, do you need my help, Bianca?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'No, Karenina. As external aid from the Engineering Force, your mission is to ensure the complete destruction of the Punishing Virus factory.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Only your secondary mission is to help us retrieve any corrupted frames.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "But, it seems like someone's impeding your work now.", 4: '2'}
